title: Enjoy the ride. Welcome to my Portafolio.
text:
Good day, dear reader. My name is Cristel Zuniga, but you can call me Kassandra, which is my second and favorite name. I am currently pursuing a masterâ€™s degree in Business Analytics at Baruch College, part of CUNY in New York City, with an expected graduation date of January 2026.
I have five years of experience in Supply Chain Management, with a focus over the past two years on data analysis in the supply side. One of my future goals is to build my own company as a business consultant, where we can work together to grow your business and compete with top companies.
